Did you know you can now search customers with URL parameters?

See who's using gmail:
[https://www.firstofficer.io/customers?email=gmail](https://www.firstofficer.io/customers?email=gmail)

Find a specific customer by their Stripe ID:
[https://www.firstofficer.io/customers?stripe_id=cus_xxx](https://www.firstofficer.io/customers?stripe_id=cus_xxx)
